FBIS4-10228 "drlat069_a_94017" FBIS-LAT-94-069 Daily Report 9 Apr 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba Rizo Views Need for `Differentiated Motivation' Rizo Views Need for `Differentiated Motivation' FL0904163194 Havana Radio Rebelde Network in Spanish 1155 GMT 9 Apr 94 FL0904163194 Havana Radio Rebelde Network Spanish BFN [Text] During a working visit to the UBPC [Basic Cooperative Production Units] El Cenizo and La Lima, Julian Rizo, member of the Politburo and first secretary of the Communist Party of Cuba in Camaguey, pointed out the need to practice differentiated motivation in every individual case, as a reflection of the effort, attendance, and results of the workers.
